  • Classes in com.jalios.jcms.plugin used by com.jalios.jcms.plugin 
    Class Description
    Plugin
    Main root class representing a Plugin.
    PluginAppender
    A log4j appender that keeps from 5 to 500 LoggingEvent inside a list for each plugins.
    It does not need any layout.
    PluginComponent
    A simple interface used to represents a declared plugin component (DataController, StoreListener...) The init() method will be called after constructor call to initialize the component.
    PluginManager
    Singleton used to manage plugin's life cycle.
    It also contains utility methods and constants for plugins.
    PluginPolicyManager
